1. Estimating LD Scores
=======================

1.1 Single LD Scores
--------------------

ldsc --bfile plink --l2 --ld-wind-cm 1 --out ld

This will produce three files
(a) ld.l2.ldscore.gz
(b) ld.l2.M
(c) ld.l2.M



1.2 Partitioned LD Scores
-------------------------

1.2.1 From annot matrix

ldsc --bfile plink --l2 --ld-wind-cm 1 --annot ldsc.annot --out ld

1.2.2 Binning continuous annotations

ldsc --bfile plink --l2 --ld-wind-cm 1 --cts-bin cts.txt 
--cts-breaks 10,20 --cts-names ANNOT --out ld

ldsc --bfile plink --l2 --ld-wind-cm 1 --cts-bin cts1.txt,cts2,txt 
--cts-breaks 10,20x10,40 --cts-names ANNOT1,ANNOT2 --out ld


2. Variance Components
